{"tid":1430084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「敵人分化系列」連續兩晚有人集中攻擊網上評論員","createTime":"2019-08-07T15:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T17:23:50.000Z","uid":73340,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8b43834528a8788374991af66e283505601361ea","tid":1430084,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:57:26.000Z","msg":"劉細良：「無大台」等鐵律能帶領抗爭行多遠？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429803</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今晚呢個post入面張圖<br />\n係YouTube度完全搵唔到城寨有呢個標題<br />\n<br />\n我係YouTube搵城寨就咁既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k6nrbwU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6nrbwU.png&h=7761e927&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyXnuiA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdyXnuiA.png&h=bd71e004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住個post唔夠1小時即刻變熱門post<br />\n有大量既鬼幫手分化<br />\n<br />\n重新幾肯定 果班評論員 係極支持無大台主意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分析敵人策略</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.首先想標籤班評論員 ，令到群眾對呢d評論員憤怒<br />\n<br />\n2.再分化一班支持者 &amp; 其他思想不同既人 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應付策略</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n<br />\n2. 扔核彈都唔會切<br />\n<br />\n3. 請不要回果邊既post or 不置頂模式<br />\n<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入返果個post起底捉鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n本身睇左幾晚分化post都算，但點知攻勢愈來愈多，所以出post 去比大家判斷"},{"pid":"1d6803173d65f0554679b054b247440e0995f01b","tid":1430084,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7adac76e6fa970199ed4c9095418b044f13c83a","tid":1430084,"uid":301